candidates.title: Update axum-extra requirement from 0.5.0 to 0.6.0

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

candidates.body:
Updates the requirements on [axum-extra](https://github.com/tokio-rs/axum) to permit the latest version.
Release notes

Sourced from axum-extra's releases.

axum-extra - v0.6.0

  • breaking: Change casing of ProtoBuf to Protobuf (#1595)

  • breaking: SpaRouter has been removed. Use ServeDir and ServeFile from tower-http instead:

    // before
Router::new().merge(SpaRouter::new("/assets", "dist"));

    // with ServeDir
Router::new().nest_service("/assets", ServeDir::new("dist"));
    

    // before with index_file
Router::new().merge(SpaRouter::new("/assets", "dist").index_file("index.html"));
    

    // with ServeDir + ServeFile
Router::new().nest_service(
"/assets",
ServeDir::new("dist").not_found_service(ServeFile::new("dist/index.html")),
);

    See the [static-file-server-example] for more examples (#1784)

#1595: tokio-rs/axum#1595 #1784: tokio-rs/axum#1784 [static-file-server-example]: https://github.com/tokio-rs/axum/blob/main/examples/static-file-server/src/main.rs

Commits
  • 08bac36 Release axum and axum-extra (#1788)
  • 279a8e2 Add example showing how to run axum on hyper 1.0 (#1791)
  • 1dc4b44 Use JsonRejection::{status, body_text} in customize extractor error example...
  • 37e2a7d docs: Clarify that state parameters need to come before body too (#1785)
  • 27f05ad Remove SpaRouter (#1784)
  • f726f16 Update to tower-http 0.4 (#1783)
  • 6a4825b Rename ProtoBuf to Protobuf (#1763)
  • 3747877 Release axum (#1782)
  • 2cbaa63 Add KeepAlive::event (#1729)
  • 1f22439 Add shared mutable state documentation (#1759)
